analysis.description:
Staking.reinvestEther (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#332-341) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- ! address(tokenContract_).call.value(_balance)() (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#334-341)

Staking.withdrawProfit (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#260-279) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-tokenContract_.transfer(_customerAddress,_profits) (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#274-277)

Staking.withdrawCapital (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#281-331) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-tokenContract_.transfer(_customerAddress,_taxedDeposit) (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#320-325)
Parameter '_from' of Staking.tokenFallback (/unique_chucks/9/0xa206d217c0642735e82a6b11547bf00659623163.sol#204-206) is not in mixedCase
